1
00:00:50,980 --> 00:00:56,220
=Go Back Lover=

2
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:00,490
=Go Back Lover=

3
00:01:03,490 --> 00:01:07,490
(Summer Break of Freshman Year,
July 2014)

4
00:01:20,550 --> 00:01:21,470
What are you doing?

5
00:01:22,830 --> 00:01:23,830
It's finally summer break.

6
00:01:24,270 --> 00:01:25,660
I can hold my girlfriend to sleep now.

7
00:01:26,550 --> 00:01:27,110
Listen,

8
00:01:27,220 --> 00:01:28,500
you better restrain yourself.

9
00:01:28,780 --> 00:01:30,190
Aunt Pei asked me

10
00:01:30,190 --> 00:01:30,990
if you're in a relationship today.

11
00:01:31,270 --> 00:01:31,830
She asked you that?

12
00:01:32,830 --> 00:01:33,740
Why is she asking this suddenly?

13
00:01:34,140 --> 00:01:35,190
How would I know?

14
00:01:35,580 --> 00:01:36,780
I think we need to find a time

15
00:01:36,780 --> 00:01:37,910
to clarify to her.

16
00:01:39,740 --> 00:01:41,070
It's not that I don't want to tell her,

17
00:01:41,380 --> 00:01:42,470
the thing is, if we do that,

18
00:01:42,830 --> 00:01:43,830
she won't stop nagging.

19
00:01:44,190 --> 00:01:45,500
Come to me when you think this through.

20
00:01:45,860 --> 00:01:47,020
Get out, now.

21
00:01:47,230 --> 00:01:48,070
I won't go.

22
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:48,830
Get out.

23
00:01:48,830 --> 00:01:50,470
Ruo, can you take a look at this?

24
00:01:59,270 --> 00:02:00,830
Is she not in here?

25
00:02:01,630 --> 00:02:03,270
I'll come back later.

26
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:10,580
Are you happy now?

27
00:02:10,740 --> 00:02:11,580
She knows everything now.

28
00:02:13,670 --> 00:02:14,300
Get out.

29
00:02:16,310 --> 00:02:17,390
Stop pushing me.

30
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:19,900
Fine, I'll go.

31
00:02:19,950 --> 00:02:21,020
I'm going to explain to her.

32
00:02:40,460 --> 00:02:41,550
Ouch.

33
00:02:42,830 --> 00:02:43,580
Do you know pain?

34
00:02:45,510 --> 00:02:46,230
This is not a dream.

35
00:02:47,390 --> 00:02:48,670
What were you doing in her room?

36
00:02:49,620 --> 00:02:50,510
Behaving like a hooligan?

37
00:02:51,110 --> 00:02:52,270
What hooligan?

38
00:02:52,510 --> 00:02:53,039
We

39
00:02:53,860 --> 00:02:54,430
are in a relationship.

40
00:02:57,790 --> 00:02:59,020
A relationship?

41
00:02:59,860 --> 00:03:00,530
You

42
00:03:01,180 --> 00:03:01,900
and Ruo?

43
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:03,180
Yes.

44
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:04,230
When did it happen?

45
00:03:05,060 --> 00:03:06,270
We've been together for a while.

46
00:03:06,390 --> 00:03:08,670
We wanted to tell you, but...

47
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:16,550
Well done.

48
00:03:17,110 --> 00:03:18,300
This is the best thing you've done

49
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:20,180
since your birth.

50
00:03:20,180 --> 00:03:21,140
Come on, tell me everything.

51
00:03:21,670 --> 00:03:22,510
When did it start?

52
00:03:22,580 --> 00:03:23,950
How did you two get together?

53
00:03:24,550 --> 00:03:25,510
What stage are you in now?

54
00:03:25,510 --> 00:03:26,710
Tell me now.

55
00:03:28,490 --> 00:03:34,770
=Episode 17=
(Love is like an uncontrollable sneeze.)

56
00:03:34,970 --> 00:03:38,450
(Year 2024)

57
00:03:38,450 --> 00:03:40,530
(Shi Qin)

58
00:03:48,860 --> 00:03:49,390
You're back.

59
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:53,390
I didn't reply to your message
fast enough today,

60
00:03:54,430 --> 00:03:55,340
are you upset?

61
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:56,710
It's fine.

62
00:04:00,740 --> 00:04:01,550
Stop eating instant noodles.

63
00:04:01,990 --> 00:04:02,620
I haven't eaten either.

64
00:04:02,990 --> 00:04:04,670
I'll make noodles so we can share,

65
00:04:04,830 --> 00:04:05,460
just like last time.

66
00:04:06,580 --> 00:04:07,430
No, thanks.

67
00:04:09,110 --> 00:04:09,710
Shi Qin?

68
00:04:10,550 --> 00:04:11,060
Shi Qin?

69
00:04:28,260 --> 00:04:30,990
You mean you sent He Siyue
a text on WeChat

70
00:04:31,230 --> 00:04:32,590
and you noticed he read it
without sending a reply

71
00:04:32,590 --> 00:04:34,030
across the road

72
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:37,230
and the reason is
that he is with Zhai Jiajing?

73
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:41,940
He Siyue, what a scumbag.

74
00:04:41,940 --> 00:04:43,110
I'll question him now.

75
00:04:43,110 --> 00:04:44,300
- What is going on?
- Don't be impulsive.

76
00:04:44,620 --> 00:04:45,380
Don't be impulsive.

77
00:04:45,740 --> 00:04:47,550
How can I not?

78
00:04:47,820 --> 00:04:48,940
Listen to Qin.

79
00:04:49,060 --> 00:04:50,550
How can he do this?

80
00:04:51,470 --> 00:04:53,940
He has demonstrated his love to her
like crazy on the show,

81
00:04:53,940 --> 00:04:56,740
yet he is dating Zhai Jiajing
in secret behind the scenes?

82
00:04:57,150 --> 00:04:58,940
What a two-faced scumbag!

83
00:04:59,110 --> 00:05:00,670
I have to seek justice for you today.

84
00:05:00,670 --> 00:05:01,820
Come back, you!

85
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:02,860
Wait a second.

86
00:05:03,260 --> 00:05:05,060
Calm down.

87
00:05:05,380 --> 00:05:07,430
We are both Qin's best friends.

88
00:05:07,820 --> 00:05:09,350
If we just rush out and question him

89
00:05:09,350 --> 00:05:10,820
but it turns out to be
a misunderstanding,

90
00:05:10,860 --> 00:05:12,670
it will make things difficult for Qin
for both sides.

91
00:05:12,990 --> 00:05:15,150
Besides, they finally got together
after so many hardships,

92
00:05:15,430 --> 00:05:16,300
if we make a fuss,

93
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,620
how are they going
to meet each other again in the future?

94
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:18,940
What should we do?

95
00:05:19,230 --> 00:05:20,820
We can't just let him off the hook.

96
00:05:25,350 --> 00:05:26,180
We won't question him,

97
00:05:26,990 --> 00:05:27,740
but

98
00:05:27,820 --> 00:05:30,300
we can get Xu Chengzhou
and Lu Xingyan do it.

99
00:05:32,620 --> 00:05:34,030
We get them to meet He Siyue

100
00:05:34,230 --> 00:05:35,500
to have a chat,

101
00:05:35,790 --> 00:05:37,380
they can probe him

102
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:40,150
to find out what's going on
with him and Zhai Jiajing.

103
00:05:42,670 --> 00:05:43,230
I second this.

104
00:05:54,990 --> 00:05:55,820
Yue, having a jog?

105
00:05:55,990 --> 00:05:56,910
Why are you up so early?

106
00:05:57,150 --> 00:05:58,380
My eyes hurt from playing games all day.

107
00:05:58,470 --> 00:05:59,300
I wanted to take a breath of fresh air.

108
00:05:59,550 --> 00:06:00,820
And elevate our friendship.

109
00:06:03,380 --> 00:06:05,030
The three of us?
Elevating our friendship?

110
00:06:06,990 --> 00:06:08,470
We realise we don't know you
well enough,

111
00:06:08,820 --> 00:06:10,150
we neglected our duty as friends.

112
00:06:11,910 --> 00:06:13,990
What specifically do you mean?

113
00:06:14,260 --> 00:06:16,110
For example, what did you do last night?

114
00:06:16,350 --> 00:06:17,260
Who were you with?

115
00:06:17,910 --> 00:06:18,860
Why are you asking this?

116
00:06:19,470 --> 00:06:20,620
Answer the questions first.

117
00:06:23,150 --> 00:06:23,790
Sorry,

118
00:06:24,990 --> 00:06:26,110
I don't want to lie,

119
00:06:26,150 --> 00:06:26,990
I really can't answer.

120
00:06:28,670 --> 00:06:29,860
If there's nothing else,

121
00:06:30,180 --> 00:06:31,300
I should go.

122
00:06:31,670 --> 00:06:32,180
Wait.

123
00:06:33,180 --> 00:06:34,060
We have known each other
for so many years.

124
00:06:34,620 --> 00:06:35,820
Is there something
you are hiding from us?

125
00:06:35,990 --> 00:06:36,579
Exactly.

126
00:06:36,860 --> 00:06:37,470
What did you do last night?

127
00:06:38,350 --> 00:06:39,150
Were you with Zhai Jiajing?

128
00:06:41,350 --> 00:06:42,700
How do you know
that I was with her yesterday?

129
00:06:43,910 --> 00:06:44,620
Don't reflect the question.

130
00:06:45,550 --> 00:06:47,230
Be honest, what did you do last night?

131
00:06:53,430 --> 00:06:54,030
Sorry,

132
00:06:55,430 --> 00:06:56,380
I can't say.

133
00:06:58,570 --> 00:06:59,370
I really can't.

134
00:07:06,940 --> 00:07:07,700
Why not?

135
00:07:08,590 --> 00:07:09,430
He doesn't need to answer,

136
00:07:12,150 --> 00:07:12,860
I'll do it for him.

137
00:07:13,230 --> 00:07:15,990
He Siyue is a complete scumbag.

138
00:07:16,550 --> 00:07:18,500
He was acting mysterious

139
00:07:18,500 --> 00:07:19,700
and hesitant.

140
00:07:20,230 --> 00:07:22,060
He must have some ulterior secret

141
00:07:22,150 --> 00:07:23,060
with Zhai Jiajing.

142
00:07:24,380 --> 00:07:25,550
Do you think

143
00:07:25,940 --> 00:07:29,230
there could be some unspeakable reason
behind this?

144
00:07:29,260 --> 00:07:30,740
Unspeakable reason?

145
00:07:31,500 --> 00:07:32,030
Qin,

146
00:07:32,030 --> 00:07:34,180
are you listening to yourself?

147
00:07:34,670 --> 00:07:36,940
Give me an example
of an unspeakable reason now.

148
00:07:36,940 --> 00:07:37,620
I want to know. Come on.

149
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:43,860
Qin,

150
00:07:43,860 --> 00:07:45,820
can you stop lying to yourself?

151
00:07:47,550 --> 00:07:51,470
I made this gin and tonic just for you.

152
00:07:52,260 --> 00:07:54,500
It appears colourless,

153
00:07:54,820 --> 00:07:56,940
but it actually has
very high alcohol content,

154
00:07:56,990 --> 00:07:57,910
it makes you tipsy easily.

155
00:07:58,350 --> 00:08:00,110
I gave it a nice name,

156
00:08:00,300 --> 00:08:01,590
"Tears of A Scumbag".

157
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:02,500
It's for you.

158
00:08:03,700 --> 00:08:05,180
"Tears of A Scumbag"?

159
00:08:05,380 --> 00:08:07,030
Why are you introducing drinks?

160
00:08:07,350 --> 00:08:08,380
This drink

161
00:08:08,550 --> 00:08:09,790
resembles He Siyue.

162
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:13,500
Simple and harmless in appearance,

163
00:08:14,590 --> 00:08:16,990
but actually very profound.

164
00:08:17,790 --> 00:08:18,350
Finish it.

165
00:08:19,820 --> 00:08:20,430
Time to wake up.

166
00:08:29,550 --> 00:08:30,430
What does this mean?

167
00:08:30,790 --> 00:08:32,470
It's an illustration that profound men

168
00:08:32,550 --> 00:08:33,790
are not suitable for you at all.

169
00:08:33,990 --> 00:08:34,500
Have some water.

170
00:08:46,030 --> 00:08:49,550
He's actually really good to me.

171
00:08:50,300 --> 00:08:51,670
Besides, I can really sense

172
00:08:51,790 --> 00:08:53,940
his concern for my well-being.

173
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:57,220
It's just that I can't understand

174
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:59,510
that his concern for me

175
00:08:59,630 --> 00:09:01,940
stems from the show's requirement

176
00:09:02,630 --> 00:09:05,580
or am I taking his chivalry

177
00:09:06,580 --> 00:09:07,460
as fondness by mistake.

178
00:09:08,630 --> 00:09:10,220
Although he never expresses

179
00:09:10,460 --> 00:09:12,180
his feelings,

180
00:09:12,300 --> 00:09:13,820
I can see it in his eyes.

181
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:15,580
I do think

182
00:09:15,790 --> 00:09:18,270
He Siyue likes Qin quite a lot.

183
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:19,130
Otherwise,

184
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:20,750
why would he be so nice to her
on the program?

185
00:09:21,700 --> 00:09:24,060
Shen Xingruo, how can you say that?

186
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:27,220
You are totally speaking for him.

187
00:09:27,550 --> 00:09:29,630
No, I just think there's something off
about this.

188
00:09:29,820 --> 00:09:32,100
If He Siyue really likes Zhai Jiajing,

189
00:09:32,220 --> 00:09:33,030
why didn't he

190
00:09:33,030 --> 00:09:34,790
join the program with our Qin
instead of her

191
00:09:34,790 --> 00:09:35,820
from the start?

192
00:09:36,430 --> 00:09:39,300
That is the trick of a scumbag, friends.

193
00:09:39,980 --> 00:09:41,580
When they get something,
they crave something else.

194
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:42,870
They are unfaithful.

195
00:09:44,220 --> 00:09:45,870
But when I actually think about it,

196
00:09:46,030 --> 00:09:46,980
I still think

197
00:09:47,390 --> 00:09:49,030
He Siyue and Zhai Jiajing

198
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:51,030
shouldn't have much
interaction in private.

199
00:09:51,270 --> 00:09:52,510
Since he's not answering anything,

200
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:53,910
let's ask Zhai Jiajing.

201
00:09:54,460 --> 00:09:55,630
No matter what,

202
00:09:55,630 --> 00:09:56,790
we need to figure this out.

203
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:58,430
We can't let Qin

204
00:09:58,550 --> 00:10:00,030
endure the pain of
a vague and unclear love.

205
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:02,230
Alright.

206
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:04,550
You two, don't worry too much about me.

207
00:10:04,940 --> 00:10:06,580
After all, this is my personal matter.

208
00:10:07,220 --> 00:10:08,790
I can still handle it properly.

209
00:10:14,460 --> 00:10:15,340
Take your time with it.

210
00:10:15,790 --> 00:10:16,980
I'll make you another one.

211
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:18,100
You're making more?

212
00:11:01,100 --> 00:11:01,910
Sorry.

213
00:11:02,820 --> 00:11:04,060
I got a call from a trainee

214
00:11:04,060 --> 00:11:05,870
about a case

215
00:11:06,060 --> 00:11:07,460
when I got out

216
00:11:07,550 --> 00:11:08,460
so I took some time.

217
00:11:08,870 --> 00:11:09,440
It's fine.

218
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:10,060
Have a seat.

219
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:12,270
You have no idea

220
00:11:12,270 --> 00:11:13,820
how troublesome are
these trainee lawyers.

221
00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:16,150
They just can't understand things
no matter how many times I tell them.

222
00:11:18,580 --> 00:11:19,510
Have you gotten
your practising license?

223
00:11:20,220 --> 00:11:20,870
I just did.

224
00:11:22,460 --> 00:11:24,270
Wait until you have trainees,

225
00:11:24,270 --> 00:11:24,870
you will understand.

226
00:11:26,150 --> 00:11:27,340
You looked me up at such a late hour,

227
00:11:27,430 --> 00:11:28,430
did something happen?

228
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:32,750
I have something
I want to talk to you about.

229
00:11:35,870 --> 00:11:37,550
(Go Back Lover)
(The ultimate choice of the challengers)

230
00:11:37,550 --> 00:11:38,460
(Challenge Mission)
(is starting soon.)

231
00:11:38,980 --> 00:11:40,150
(Dear guests, please take your seats.)

232
00:11:40,790 --> 00:11:42,820
(This round will feature
a guest mutual voting session.)

233
00:11:43,300 --> 00:11:45,030
(Challenger, Guest)
(Challengers are allowed to pick)

234
00:11:45,030 --> 00:11:46,180
(any guest of the opposite gender)

235
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:48,870
(and guests can make a pick)

236
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:50,580
(between existing guests
and challengers.)

237
00:11:51,180 --> 00:11:53,180
(If the guest and the challenger)

238
00:11:53,180 --> 00:11:54,340
(select each other,)

239
00:11:54,510 --> 00:11:56,340
(it will be deemed that the challenge
is successful.)

240
00:11:58,910 --> 00:12:00,430
Let's welcome our two challengers

241
00:12:00,430 --> 00:12:02,060
and our three pairs of guests

242
00:12:02,390 --> 00:12:04,300
to the moment of the final choice.

243
00:12:05,030 --> 00:12:05,610
Firstly,

244
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:07,460
the two challengers

245
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:08,630
can make their choice.

246
00:12:09,460 --> 00:12:10,100
Mr. Yu Si,

247
00:12:10,910 --> 00:12:11,670
have you made your choice?

248
00:12:12,580 --> 00:12:13,150
Yes.

249
00:12:14,430 --> 00:12:15,820
I can announce it now, right?

250
00:12:16,820 --> 00:12:17,430
You may start now.

251
00:12:26,790 --> 00:12:27,460
Ms. Shi Qin,

252
00:12:30,700 --> 00:12:32,670
if I were to compare you to a flower,

253
00:12:32,670 --> 00:12:35,430
I think it would be
a lily of the valley.

254
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:38,150
Quiet, gentle,

255
00:12:38,790 --> 00:12:39,510
pure, and, flawless.

256
00:12:40,700 --> 00:12:41,700
When I am by your side,

257
00:12:41,700 --> 00:12:43,340
I can feel absolute peace.

258
00:12:44,270 --> 00:12:45,580
No one else can give me this feeling.

259
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:48,940
Therefore, you have to be confident
in yourself.

260
00:12:52,300 --> 00:12:53,750
However, sorry,

261
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:54,820
you are not my choice.

262
00:13:03,980 --> 00:13:04,790
Ms. Chen Zhu,

263
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:07,940
you are passionate and beautiful

264
00:13:08,510 --> 00:13:09,820
just like champagne roses
that you love.

265
00:13:10,460 --> 00:13:12,390
Your emotions infect those around you,

266
00:13:13,390 --> 00:13:13,910
including me.

267
00:13:14,820 --> 00:13:15,940
When I'm with you,

268
00:13:15,940 --> 00:13:17,630
indeed, I laugh out loud

269
00:13:17,630 --> 00:13:18,910
involuntarily.

270
00:13:19,670 --> 00:13:20,300
Indeed,

271
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:22,430
I can't control

272
00:13:22,430 --> 00:13:23,670
my true inner emotions.

273
00:13:24,630 --> 00:13:26,700
You are a girl who is very worthy
of being liked

274
00:13:29,060 --> 00:13:29,630
but don't worry,

275
00:13:30,430 --> 00:13:31,340
I won't choose you either.

276
00:13:40,910 --> 00:13:41,630
Nervous?

277
00:13:43,460 --> 00:13:44,300
If you have something to say,
say it quickly.

278
00:13:46,060 --> 00:13:47,300
When I'm with you,

279
00:13:47,460 --> 00:13:48,300
all I do is deprecate you.

280
00:13:48,300 --> 00:13:48,980
To praise you

281
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:51,750
