00:27:00,830 --> 00:27:01,460
why didn't your father

562
00:27:02,740 --> 00:27:03,590
want us two back then?

563
00:27:07,150 --> 00:27:08,110
Answer it!

564
00:27:12,830 --> 00:27:14,110
It's because I am a girl,

565
00:27:16,700 --> 00:27:18,070
he wanted a son.

566
00:27:22,740 --> 00:27:23,870
I almost lost my life

567
00:27:25,670 --> 00:27:26,980
when I gave birth to you.

568
00:27:31,020 --> 00:27:32,180
It's because of you

569
00:27:33,260 --> 00:27:35,390
that I have no chance to have a son.

570
00:27:36,260 --> 00:27:37,980
That is why your father abandoned me!

571
00:27:39,350 --> 00:27:41,110
Everyone says you bring bad luck,

572
00:27:41,460 --> 00:27:42,940
nobody likes you at all.

573
00:27:43,430 --> 00:27:44,350
It was me,

574
00:27:44,910 --> 00:27:47,070
it was me who raised you up
with my own hands.

575
00:27:47,980 --> 00:27:48,910
It has been so many years,

576
00:27:49,220 --> 00:27:51,670
I played the role of a father
and a mother at the same time,

577
00:27:53,540 --> 00:27:54,150
do you think it was easy for me?

578
00:27:55,390 --> 00:27:56,020
I know.

579
00:27:57,740 --> 00:27:59,870
I know it is difficult for you, Mom.

580
00:28:01,430 --> 00:28:05,260
I work extremely long hours
and maintained a frugal lifestyle

581
00:28:06,390 --> 00:28:07,590
to buy you a piano

582
00:28:08,910 --> 00:28:10,430
and enrol you on tuition classes.

583
00:28:12,780 --> 00:28:13,740
What am I after?

584
00:28:15,940 --> 00:28:17,020
What is it that I want?

585
00:28:17,310 --> 00:28:18,670
You want me to study well

586
00:28:18,830 --> 00:28:19,830
and to have a good future

587
00:28:19,830 --> 00:28:21,180
so we can uplift each other.

588
00:28:21,180 --> 00:28:22,260
Did you do it?

589
00:28:22,980 --> 00:28:24,310
What is your repayment?

590
00:28:25,110 --> 00:28:26,350
Sorry, Mom.

591
00:28:26,350 --> 00:28:28,390
I will try harder. I'm sorry.

592
00:28:28,700 --> 00:28:30,590
You say that every time.

593
00:28:31,310 --> 00:28:33,070
If I knew you'd be like this,

594
00:28:33,540 --> 00:28:35,940
I shouldn't have given birth
to you in the first place.

595
00:28:36,870 --> 00:28:38,020
What brings you,
this karmic retribution,

596
00:28:38,150 --> 00:28:39,460
to my side?

597
00:28:54,980 --> 00:28:55,560
Mom,

598
00:28:57,150 --> 00:28:58,020
sorry.

599
00:29:00,590 --> 00:29:02,460
If I had a choice,

600
00:29:05,460 --> 00:29:07,430
I wouldn't want to come
to this world either.

601
00:29:07,430 --> 00:29:08,150
What did you say?

602
00:29:14,260 --> 00:29:15,460
You have never praised me once

603
00:29:16,980 --> 00:29:19,670
since my childhood.

604
00:29:21,910 --> 00:29:23,500
When I was little, I thought

605
00:29:24,310 --> 00:29:25,630
it must be because I wasn't good enough

606
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:27,910
and as long as I worked harder

607
00:29:28,430 --> 00:29:29,260
and became more excellent,

608
00:29:29,980 --> 00:29:32,110
you would definitely like me

609
00:29:32,110 --> 00:29:33,630
and praise me.

610
00:29:33,980 --> 00:29:35,390
Have you forgotten what you understood

611
00:29:35,590 --> 00:29:36,590
when you were a kid, then?

612
00:29:36,590 --> 00:29:37,670
That's because I now know

613
00:29:37,670 --> 00:29:39,540
that regardless of how well I do,
it's no use.

614
00:29:44,070 --> 00:29:45,260
Zhai Jiajing, listen.

615
00:29:45,910 --> 00:29:47,430
As long as you stay in this house,

616
00:29:47,910 --> 00:29:48,940
no matter what I do to you,

617
00:29:49,430 --> 00:29:50,430
you have to bear with it.

618
00:29:50,430 --> 00:29:51,670
I'm done!

619
00:29:52,700 --> 00:29:53,670
I finally understand.

620
00:29:54,150 --> 00:29:56,220
Both you and your father
can never be tamed like wolves.

621
00:29:56,540 --> 00:29:58,150
Get out! Leave!

622
00:29:58,740 --> 00:29:59,870
Go as far away as you can!

623
00:29:59,870 --> 00:30:00,940
This house doesn't need you!

624
00:30:01,180 --> 00:30:02,590
Go!

625
00:30:03,070 --> 00:30:04,310
As far away as you can!

626
00:31:18,740 --> 00:31:19,390
Zhai Jiajing!

627
00:31:20,260 --> 00:31:20,940
Zhai Jiajing!

628
00:31:25,740 --> 00:31:28,180
Let go!

629
00:31:29,310 --> 00:31:30,700
Let me go!

630
00:31:30,700 --> 00:31:31,780
He Siyue, let me go!

631
00:31:31,780 --> 00:31:33,350
- Have you gone mad?
- Let go!

632
00:31:33,350 --> 00:31:34,220
Zhai Jiajing, calm down!

633
00:31:36,020 --> 00:31:37,940
Calm down.

634
00:31:41,180 --> 00:31:42,110
Don't die today.

635
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:44,350
If you really want to die,

636
00:31:45,110 --> 00:31:45,830
do it on another day.

637
00:31:46,070 --> 00:31:46,940
Just see this as lending the day to me,

638
00:31:47,950 --> 00:31:48,590
can you?

639
00:32:16,220 --> 00:32:18,870
I heard everything about the fight

640
00:32:19,260 --> 00:32:20,460
between you and your mother today.

641
00:32:24,870 --> 00:32:25,590
How ridiculous.

642
00:32:27,830 --> 00:32:28,540
Before this,

643
00:32:30,430 --> 00:32:32,020
I wanted to surpass you,
even in my dreams.

644
00:32:33,540 --> 00:32:34,460
It turns out,

645
00:32:36,180 --> 00:32:36,870
you are now in second place

646
00:32:38,220 --> 00:32:38,830
and I am third.

647
00:32:41,780 --> 00:32:43,150
You even saw me like this.

648
00:32:45,310 --> 00:32:46,310
Don't think this way.

649
00:32:46,700 --> 00:32:48,220
School results don't mean anything.

650
00:32:48,220 --> 00:32:49,830
It is everything to me.

651
00:32:59,460 --> 00:33:01,540
I pretend to be cheerful

652
00:33:02,830 --> 00:33:04,630
at school every day

653
00:33:06,430 --> 00:33:08,870
as if I don't care
about my results at all,

654
00:33:11,670 --> 00:33:14,590
as if I'm a little princess
spoilt by my parents.

655
00:33:17,350 --> 00:33:18,350
I am not happy.

656
00:33:21,180 --> 00:33:22,590
I am so tired.

657
00:33:32,870 --> 00:33:33,870
He Siyue,

658
00:33:38,310 --> 00:33:39,150
the real me

659
00:33:41,500 --> 00:33:43,670
is even more pathetic than
what you're looking at now.

660
00:33:53,020 --> 00:33:53,590
Don't worry,

661
00:33:55,630 --> 00:33:56,910
I will help you keep this secret.

662
00:34:00,830 --> 00:34:01,350
Really?

663
00:34:04,430 --> 00:34:05,020
Zhai Jiajing,

664
00:34:06,780 --> 00:34:08,740
I won't tell anyone about this.

665
00:34:09,590 --> 00:34:11,390
I will also keep this a secret.

666
00:34:12,980 --> 00:34:13,750
Trust me.

667
00:34:22,170 --> 00:34:27,330
(Freshman Year, Year 2015)

668
00:34:42,310 --> 00:34:42,910
Sorry

669
00:34:43,430 --> 00:34:44,140
for being late.

670
00:34:44,910 --> 00:34:46,620
It's fine, I was just reading.

671
00:34:56,100 --> 00:34:58,020
Didn't you sleep well?

672
00:35:00,060 --> 00:35:01,430
Why do you look so haggard?

673
00:35:06,020 --> 00:35:07,350
I had difficulty falling asleep

674
00:35:09,270 --> 00:35:10,310
recently.

675
00:35:11,540 --> 00:35:12,500
I keep having dreams,

676
00:35:13,710 --> 00:35:15,230
I dreamed about many things
from the past,

677
00:35:15,910 --> 00:35:16,710
I dreamed

678
00:35:18,590 --> 00:35:19,270
about my mother.

679
00:35:26,230 --> 00:35:26,750
Zhai Jiajing,

680
00:35:28,620 --> 00:35:29,460
I think

681
00:35:30,540 --> 00:35:32,100
you should let the past go by.

682
00:35:33,140 --> 00:35:33,870
You should stop thinking about it.

683
00:35:36,750 --> 00:35:37,580
What do you want to drink?

684
00:35:41,540 --> 00:35:42,140
What's happened to your wrist?

685
00:35:48,100 --> 00:35:48,750
Did someone bully you?

686
00:35:51,870 --> 00:35:52,660
Zhai Jiajing?

687
00:35:53,870 --> 00:35:55,460
What happened? Tell me.

688
00:35:56,980 --> 00:35:57,620
I...

689
00:36:01,580 --> 00:36:02,270
I did it to myself.

690
00:36:05,460 --> 00:36:06,980
I don't know what is wrong with me.

691
00:36:08,870 --> 00:36:11,190
I just feel so suffocated inside.

692
00:36:12,870 --> 00:36:14,190
It feels like this is the only thing
I can do

693
00:36:15,310 --> 00:36:16,940
to make myself feel better.

694
00:36:22,870 --> 00:36:23,870
I hope you

695
00:36:24,980 --> 00:36:25,710
don't mind me saying this,

696
00:36:26,980 --> 00:36:27,620
I really think

697
00:36:27,620 --> 00:36:29,500
you should consult a psychiatrist.

698
00:36:30,270 --> 00:36:32,140
You can't keep being like this.

699
00:36:33,710 --> 00:36:35,980
I think I should, too,

700
00:36:39,020 --> 00:36:39,910
but I'm scared.

701
00:36:41,270 --> 00:36:43,500
I can't bring myself to go to a doctor.

702
00:36:45,750 --> 00:36:47,190
Can you go with me?

703
00:36:48,980 --> 00:36:49,580
Can you do that?

704
00:36:54,620 --> 00:36:55,430
Please?

705
00:37:04,390 --> 00:37:07,190
Fine, I'll go with you.

706
00:37:14,870 --> 00:37:15,790
All these years,

707
00:37:17,230 --> 00:37:18,790
you have always been by my side.

708
00:37:20,020 --> 00:37:21,660
When I was about to crumble,

709
00:37:23,660 --> 00:37:25,190
it was you who stayed with me
all the time.

710
00:37:26,460 --> 00:37:27,980
You've given me support
and encouragement.

711
00:37:30,870 --> 00:37:33,230
It's because of you that I have
the courage to live on.

712
00:37:34,620 --> 00:37:35,940
If you were not with me...

713
00:37:46,140 --> 00:37:47,350
The relationship between

714
00:37:48,710 --> 00:37:49,940
the two of us

715
00:37:49,940 --> 00:37:51,870
is not something
that others can understand.

716
00:37:55,790 --> 00:37:57,460
Stop deceiving yourself.

717
00:37:59,660 --> 00:38:01,460
You have feelings for me.

718
00:38:07,270 --> 00:38:07,940
Zhai Jiajing,

719
00:38:10,500 --> 00:38:11,060
I'm sorry.

720
00:38:12,100 --> 00:38:13,310
I have no feelings for you.

721
00:38:14,940 --> 00:38:16,500
Besides, I already have someone I like.

722
00:38:18,060 --> 00:38:19,020
I can't accept you.

723
00:39:12,060 --> 00:39:13,980
Qin, are you alright?

724
00:39:14,580 --> 00:39:15,310
Wherever you are,

725
00:39:15,310 --> 00:39:16,790
please text me back now.

726
00:39:17,140 --> 00:39:17,980
I'm worried about you.

727
00:39:22,390 --> 00:39:23,390
(Shi Qin)
(Don't worry.)

728
00:39:23,540 --> 00:39:24,230
(I'm fine.)

729
00:39:24,940 --> 00:39:25,940
(I just want to be alone.)

730
00:39:34,910 --> 00:39:35,510
Hello.

731
00:40:01,830 --> 00:40:02,540
What's up with you?

732
00:40:02,870 --> 00:40:03,870
You didn't even notice when I arrived.

733
00:40:04,230 --> 00:40:04,790
Nothing,

734
00:40:06,350 --> 00:40:06,870
I was just waiting for you.

735
00:40:07,540 --> 00:40:08,460
Are you done with work?

736
00:40:10,100 --> 00:40:12,270
I wanted to invite Qin
to dinner tonight,

737
00:40:12,790 --> 00:40:14,830
but she said she wanted to be alone,

738
00:40:14,980 --> 00:40:15,620
so I came over.

739
00:40:26,940 --> 00:40:27,940
Why aren't you eating?

740
00:40:29,100 --> 00:40:31,270
I felt something was off
as soon as I came in.

741
00:40:31,790 --> 00:40:34,020
What is wrong with you today?

742
00:40:35,580 --> 00:40:36,230
Eat up.

743
00:40:36,710 --> 00:40:37,460
I won't eat if you don't tell me.

744
00:40:46,870 --> 00:40:48,620
Xu Chengzhou told me something today.

745
00:40:50,750 --> 00:40:52,350
The resort has received a new event.

746
00:40:53,500 --> 00:40:55,140
An event? Isn't that good news?

747
00:40:56,430 --> 00:40:57,270
This event

748
00:40:58,390 --> 00:41:00,940
is a funeral.

749
00:41:04,310 --> 00:41:05,500
Whose funeral is it?

750
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:11,620
It's your father's funeral.

751
00:41:25,140 --> 00:41:25,830
My father...

752
00:41:28,310 --> 00:41:28,870
He...

753
00:41:35,020 --> 00:41:36,230
When did it happen?

754
00:41:37,540 --> 00:41:38,580
Uncle had cancer.

755
00:41:38,830 --> 00:41:40,460
He likely passed away
due to complications

756
00:41:41,270 --> 00:41:42,540
while receiving treatment abroad.

757
00:41:43,500 --> 00:41:44,140
This is everything I know

758
00:41:44,790 --> 00:41:45,870
so far.

759
00:41:49,650 --> 00:41:50,239
He...

760
00:41:51,750 --> 00:41:52,790
When will he return here?

761
00:41:54,940 --> 00:41:56,460
Returning the body here
would be very complicated,

762
00:41:57,140 --> 00:42:00,140
so his family

763
00:42:01,350 --> 00:42:02,980
agreed to have him cremated there.

764
00:42:04,190 --> 00:42:06,020
She will return here with his ashes,

765
00:42:07,350 --> 00:42:09,390
the funeral ceremony will be held
at the resort.

766
00:42:30,230 --> 00:42:32,100
I don't know how to comfort you,

767
00:42:33,270 --> 00:42:34,100
but I want to tell you

768
00:42:34,980 --> 00:42:35,910
that no matter what happens,

769
00:42:38,270 --> 00:42:39,270
I will always be with you.

770
00:42:45,230 --> 00:42:46,190
I'm a little exhausted,

771
00:42:49,540 --> 00:42:50,620
I should go home.

772
00:42:55,460 --> 00:42:57,310
Sure, I'll send you back.

773
00:43:14,170 --> 00:43:17,850
(Go Back Lover)
(Interview Time)

774
00:43:19,250 --> 00:43:20,930
Why are you quitting the show?

775
00:43:26,530 --> 00:43:29,250
It's actually good to quit.

776
00:43:30,090 --> 00:43:31,330
Participating in this program

777
00:43:31,730 --> 00:43:32,930
has been a fantasy

778
00:43:32,930 --> 00:43:34,290
to me from the start.

779
00:43:36,010 --> 00:43:37,210
It's time to wake up.

780
00:43:38,970 --> 00:43:40,130
It's good

781
00:43:40,410 --> 00:43:43,250
that I at least got an answer

782
00:43:43,250 --> 00:43:44,850
and I can give up

783
00:43:45,370 --> 00:43:46,690
on some of my unnecessary thoughts.

784
00:43:47,890 --> 00:43:49,250
He and Zhai Jiajing

785
00:43:50,010 --> 00:43:51,810
make a good couple.

786
00:43:53,010 --> 00:43:54,050
They have always been

787
00:43:54,050 --> 00:43:56,450
the right person for each other.

788
00:43:58,290 --> 00:43:59,170
They have my blessing.

789
00:44:00,650 --> 00:44:02,010
(What do you think about Shi Qin?)
I don't know how to provide her

790
00:44:02,010 --> 00:44:03,810
a better explanation about this matter.

791
00:44:04,250 --> 00:44:05,930
If we had to do it all over again,

792
00:44:06,290 --> 00:44:07,530
I will definitely still choose her

793
00:44:07,530 --> 00:44:08,930
to participate in the show together.

794
00:44:09,410 --> 00:44:10,770
I will also definitely choose her

795
00:44:10,770 --> 00:44:12,250
to be my interested guest.

796
00:44:12,930 --> 00:44:13,730
It's just that...

797
00:44:15,530 --> 00:44:16,610
It's just that I really don't want her

798
00:44:16,610 --> 00:44:17,930
to quit the program like this.

799
00:44:19,360 --> 00:44:24,360
=Go Back Lover=

